law.text: Each limited liability partnership and each foreign limited liability partnership authorized to transact business in the Commonwealth shall continuously maintain in this Commonwealth a registered office and a registered agent that comply with KRS 14A.4-010.
law.history: Repealed, reenacted, and amended 2010 Ky. Acts ch. 151, sec. 95, effective January 1, 2011. -- Created 2006 Ky. Acts ch. 149, sec. 17, effective July 12, 2006.
